description: AMUNDI ETF MSCI WORLD EX EMU UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI World ex EMU* Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to around 1400 stocks worldwide except countries of the Economic and Monetary Union, with a single transaction. * EMU: Economic and Monetary Union. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi ETF MSCI World Ex EMU UCITS ETF
